      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CALL ME SNUGGLES (1) missed the frame last time but prior to that was an effortless Grade 5 winner (22.91) at this track, scoring by 2.5 lengths. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Can turn form around here. GOT A PUNCH (2) clocked a new course and distance PB last time, finishing a 4.5 lengths second behind Making Gems in 23.19. Top run latest and rates a key player again. AUSSIE RUSH (8) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing 10 from 20 starts. Finished in the minors latest when third (18.49) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Expected to be in this for a long way. TELL ME WHERE (5) is in the mix after placing here at this trip last time out.",
